# Capsule payload drop zone.
#
# Drop a WAD here to override the shareware default and `ldoom build` stages it into
# the image at /home/app/app. NONE of it is committed: the payload is per-user, and
# this project never ships a WAD or a binary in git (the shareware DOOM1.WAD is
# fetched at build time). Only the docs are tracked, so the directory stays in the repo.
*
!.gitignore
!README.md
